### 健康檢查
GET http://localhost:8787/

### 取得所有 todos
GET http://localhost:8787/api/todos

### 建立新 todo
POST http://localhost:8787/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "學習 Cloudflare Workers",
  "description": "使用 Hono 框架建立 API",
  "completed": false
}

### 建立另一個 todo
POST http://localhost:8787/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "學習 D1 資料庫",
  "description": "整合 SQLite 資料庫",
  "completed": false
}

### 取得單一 todo (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1

### 更新 todo (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
PUT http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "學習 Cloudflare Workers (已更新)",
  "description": "使用 Hono 框架建立 API - 已完成",
  "completed": true
}

### 切換 todo 完成狀態 (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1/toggle

### 刪除 todo (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1
